<section class="roadmap">
  <h2>Our Roadmap</h2>
  <p class="description">
    It can be hard to get something done, there are an infinite number of distractions so we have a detailed roadmap that we follow to build Silicon Prairie.
  </p>

  <ul class="stages">
    <li class="stage">
      <h3>
        Growth
      </h3>
      <h6>Stage 1</h6>
      <p>
        Build a strong community that is charged and shares a common vision for the future.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Collaborate, encourage, and sponsor independent tech events.</li>
        <li>Seek out community pillar involvement.</li>
        <li>Start bi-weekly Interface Fargo event.</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li class="stage active">
      <h3>
        Improvement
      </h3>
      <h6>Stage 2</h6>
      <p>
        Supplement and encourage growth in underdeveloped areas.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Plan and host educational workshops.</li>
        <li>Organize hackathons and conferences.</li>
        <li>Challenge the community to reach new heights.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="progress-bar">
        <div class="progress"></div>
      </div>
      <h6>25% Progress to next stage</h6>

      <ul class="tasks">
        <li><i class="fa fa-square-o"></i> Host 5 conferences <small>0/5</small></li>
        <li><i class="fa fa-square-o"></i> Engage 10 Partners <small><%= Partner.count %>/10</small></li>
        <li><i class="fa fa-square-o"></i> Sponsor 50 Events <small><%= Event.count %>/50</small></li>
        <li><i class="fa fa-square-o"></i> Reach 250 Members <small><%= User.count %>/250</small></li>
      </ul>

      <p class="actions">
        <%= render partial: "layouts/shared/become_a_partner" %>
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="stage">
      <h3>
        Education
      </h3>
      <h6>Stage 3</h6>
      <p>
        Maintain the momentum over the long term through education.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Encourage cutting edge cirriculums at local institutions.</li>
        <li>Plan and host world-class technology bootcamps.</li>
        <li>Maintain the best tech community in the world.</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>
